&lt;li&gt;Maintain the office seating chart and support forward-looking space planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with office moves, fit-out activity, and refurbishment coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate meetings and onsite logistics as needed, including agendas, minutes, space reservations, catering, and vendor coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
